The project is about helping users understand the basics of online safety through simple interaction conversation.
When the program starts, it will play a greeting audio and display an ACSII logo.
The users will be able to chat to the bot by typing safety related questions such as phishing, password and web browsing.
Here are the commands to say to the bot: How are you
                                         Purpose
                                         Password
                                         Phishing
                                         Browsing
                                         Malware
                                         Privacy
                                         Wifi
The functionalities that are present is the displayng of the ASCII logo, the greeting audio,
colouring of the words and bot rsponses.
